author: Lauren Moraski CBS News
title: Brooklyn Decker and Andy Roddick welcome baby
text:
Andy Roddick and Brooklyn Decker have welcomed their first child together.
33 Photos The stork club Their babies are born with silver spoons in their mouths and stars in their eyes
Us Weekly reports that the actress and her tennis player husband are now parents to a baby boy, born in Austin, Texas, last week.
No word yet on the little one's name.
Decker divulged the pregnancy news earlier this year, writing on Instagram: "So this happened ... #the3ofus."
She has since shared plenty of baby bump photos on social media.
My butt has just folded itself into my belly. And my boobs are officially resting on my gut. We're in the homestretch, y'all. Photo courtesy of my sort-of-tv-step-brother @barvonblaq @graceandfrankie
A photo posted by Brooklyn Decker (@brooklyndecker) on Sep 3, 2015 at 6:01pm PDT
Flannel in the front, denim in the back... My kinda party. THANK YOU @jessiejamesdecker for this treat!! It's one of the few things I can still fit into, and look forward to wearing after üçº! You're a rockstar mama, singer, AND clothing designer. xx
A photo posted by Brooklyn Decker (@brooklyndecker) on Sep 18, 2015 at 11:06am PDT
Now we await a photo of the pair's latest addition.
Decker, 28, married Roddick, 33, started dating in 2007 and were married in 2009.
